MNote2 is a simple graphic text editor.
MNote2 is the abbreviation for de Maurin Editor 2.
The Editor is an open source project, and can be easily downloaded from git: https://github.com/MarceloMaurin/MNote2 .

For more information about the project, visit the project's blog:
http://maurinsoft.com.br/index.php/projeto-mnote2/
